headline: Fifth Third Plans More Crypto After Five Years Studying Assets
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Fifth Third Bancorp. began forging relationships with crypto companies about five years ago, but held off on major investments until regulation became clearer. That moment has arrived, according to the bank’s head of strategy.
